The exercises are prepared for complete beginners.

How the exercises work
  Execute them 
    bash exercise_01.bash

  Follow the instructions on screen
    ==================================================
    Write a program that converts a tuple to list.
    The program must have one exported function exercise_01/1

    Example
    ==================================================
	    MODULE_NAME:exercise_01({1,2,3}) returns [1,2,3].


    Verification of the exercise
    ==================================================
    You can verify your answer using your answer file as an argument to the option f.
	   bash exercise_01.bash -f ANSWER_FILE


  